    <div class="review-txt-outer">
        <div class="review-txt ">
            Great program with levels from very easy to insanely difficult.  Unique feature is the &#39;Extended Print&#39;
I use this to print 2 puzzles per page. 5 pages at a time, then turn over the stack and print 2 per page on the other side.  Select &#39;Extended Print&#39; from file menu. select 2 per page in layout, then fill in each section eg number puzzles &#39;2&#39;; Difficulty &#39;Hard&#39; then use slider on right to go to next section (5 sections in all) In 2 or 3 minutes with laser printer and I have 20 puzzles to take with me.
        </div>
    </div>

    
